anger in clinging    danger in being    danger in birth   In how many aspects is there danger in ageinganddeath In how many aspects does ageinganddeath ceaseThere is danger in ageinganddeath in five aspects Ageinganddeath ceases I shall breathe out contemplating the cessation of ageingand deathThrough inbreaths and outbreaths contemplating cessation there are ideas The establishment Hence Development of the Foundation of Mindfulness consisting in contemplation of ideas as ideas is saidRelinquishment there are two kinds of relinquishment relinquishment as giving up and relinquishment as entering into It gives up materiality thus it is relinquishment as giving upIt gives up feeling  and so on with the rest of the  ideas listed in Tr I  up to Through inbreaths and outbreaths contemplating relinquishment there are ideas The establishment Hence Development of the Foundation of Mindfulness consisting in contemplation of ideas as ideas is saidEight kinds of knowledge of contemplation and eight kinds of establishment of mindfulness Four grounds from the Sutta dealing with contemplation of ideas as ideasThese are the thirtytwo kinds of knowledge in mindful workershe trains thus I shall breathe in contemplating impermanence in feeling  and so on with the rest of the  ideas listed in Tr I  up to he trains thus I shall breathe out contemplating impermanence in ageinganddeathDevelopment Inbreaths and outbreaths contemplating impermanence are Purification of Virtue as restraint   When he understands unification of cognizance and nondistraction through inbreaths and outbreaths contemplating impermanence his feelings are recognized as they arise  When he understands unification of cognizance and nondistraction through inbreaths and outbreaths contemplating impermanence he combines the facultiesHow is it that he trains thus Ishall breathe in contemplating fading away of greed he trains thus I shall breathe out contemplating fading away of greedhe trains thus I shall breathe in conte